# .claude/ — ignore everything by default. Each WAGF-shared skill must be
# explicitly re-included by NAME below. We do NOT broadly unignore
# `.claude/skills/**` because that would expose user-level Antigravity
# skills (frontend-design, canvas-design, etc.) which are not project
# content. Per-developer state (settings.json, plans/) stays ignored.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
.claude/skills/*
